{"tid":1564540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）如何令唱歌活動不膠化？","createTime":"2019-09-12T22:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T13:46:44.000Z","uid":85743,"like":6,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"502dffdf710d3e0bfcc56f90bde880dca3376eaf","tid":1564540,"uid":85743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"呢個星期，唱歌副本成功帶起熱潮，大家個腦都無時無刻哼起呢首，屬於我地香港的歌。<br />\n<br />\n不過亦有唔少手足擔心，唱歌嘉年華化，對政權冇威脅性。<br />\n<br />\n其實，我哋唱呢首歌時的感動，來自心底裏的身分認同，香港人呢個民族逐漸成形。呢樣嘢，正正係中共最擔心嘅！絕對唔係無威脅性（你睇d愛國力量衝岀嚟唱國歌就知。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而我地必須要正視嘉年華化呢個問題！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n留意到大家唱《願榮光歸於香港》時「各有各做」，有啲會揮動手機上的電筒光，好似演唱會咁。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為，嚴肅係必須的（諗起眾多被捕手足，一定笑唔岀）。另外，亦應該展現岀團結，勇於對抗到底的精神（做前線的堅強後盾）。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望大家投票，統一奏唱時嘅動作，取得共識後再岀文宣教育其他市民。<br />\n<br />\n高舉右手：正皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvEiq7j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvEiq7j.jpg&h=3716a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zfmoT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zfmoT0.png&h=2d2ca74b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Wj2SNm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Wj2SNm.jpg&h=4b0ec29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手擺心口：負皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZ1kEss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZ1kEss.jpg&h=d5c63d98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9N3T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9N3T8.jpg&h=d31e8ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8Scvy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8Scvy9.jpg&h=a56fc2ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家照舊當唱下歌仔，就當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b0d3594e3b9c0d88233f1db3429f1fd4b46f4c","tid":1564540,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:24:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0da911e72faddf6e89162616999ac87dd543c829","tid":1564540,"uid":4105,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:41:56.000Z","msg":"唱完收皮其實係無問題<br />\n不過一唱就成粒鐘起跳<br />\n仲要拍晒手掌<br />\n最有問題嘅唔係唱歌<br />\n係啲人嘅心態<br />\n你要知道永遠有班人係出嚟打卡<br />\n有班人當買贖罪劵<br />\n有啲人得一腔熱血<br />\n但係佢哋就會騎劫咗成件事<br />\n<br />\n沙田嗰日搞完嘉年華<br />\n絕大部分mtr走嘅人都係照拍八達通<br />\n咁你就可以知道其實對佢哋講再多都係無用<br />\n因為佢哋係活喺他佢哋自成一角嘅同溫層<br />\n所以無嘢好講"},{"pid":"aca2284118ae84e7170f37fe631433f757cfc0c0","tid":1564540,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"唱歌真係無問題，問題在於⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dcb8abbb33494eb448768027e73ab10ff0f81ae","tid":1564540,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0da911e72faddf6e89162616999ac87dd543c829","tid":1564540,"uid":4105,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:41:56.000Z","msg":"唱完收皮其實係無問題<br />\n不過一唱就成粒鐘起跳<br />\n仲要拍晒手掌<br />\n最有問題嘅唔係唱歌<br />\n係啲人嘅心態<br />\n你要知道永遠有班人係出嚟打卡<br />\n有班人當買贖罪劵<br />\n有啲人得一腔熱血<br />\n但係佢哋就會騎劫咗成件事<br />\n<br />\n沙田嗰日搞完嘉年華<br />\n絕大部分mtr走嘅人都係照拍八達通<br />\n咁你就可以知道其實對佢哋講再多都係無用<br />\n因為佢哋係活喺他佢哋自成一角嘅同溫層<br />\n所以無嘢好講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:45:05.000Z","msg":"未打完撳錯掣<br />\n你就算投完票<br />\n佢哋都未必會跟<br />\n佢哋會反問你點解唔可以各有各做<br />\n仲有啲真係路過過嚟湊熱鬧嘅<br />\n就更加無可能叫得喐"},{"pid":"a20936c7da6f17cf0b4120e586c4412f17f68685","tid":1564540,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:47:23.000Z","msg":"希望你可以幫我share呢篇文, 我知呢篇文好長, 如果唔想睇曬既話入黎睇下堆subheading都好, 我好有信心呢篇文係可以幫助打破現況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f6ed32e4d67ffdf445b22cf262fdf08430b9b5b4","tid":1564540,"uid":246640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:50:57.000Z","msg":"講真 唱唔係問題  <br />\n咁多人 咪 貼埋文宣  <br />\n平時 2~3 丁友你就驚姐  <br />\n減輕 文宣組壓力都好呀~"},{"pid":"2f25e6897f713e959df4449a5508d05c2f28f968","tid":1564540,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:51:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=f8eeed9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"9927719d35e30c45991cf4b3b5c7c342ccc85ec9","tid":1564540,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:54:57.000Z","msg":"post more on your thoughts. <br />\n<br />\ngood reminder."},{"pid":"a736876b6de07d04f7388abaf15967c285bdb7f1","tid":1564540,"uid":85743,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0da911e72faddf6e89162616999ac87dd543c829","tid":1564540,"uid":4105,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:41:56.000Z","msg":"唱完收皮其實係無問題<br />\n不過一唱就成粒鐘起跳<br />\n仲要拍晒手掌<br />\n最有問題嘅唔係唱歌<br />\n係啲人嘅心態<br />\n你要知道永遠有班人係出嚟打卡<br />\n有班人當買贖罪劵<br />\n有啲人得一腔熱血<br />\n但係佢哋就會騎劫咗成件事<br />\n<br />\n沙田嗰日搞完嘉年華<br />\n絕大部分mtr走嘅人都係照拍八達通<br />\n咁你就可以知道其實對佢哋講再多都係無用<br />\n因為佢哋係活喺他佢哋自成一角嘅同溫層<br />\n所以無嘢好講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:03:23.000Z","msg":"或者咁講，<br />\n100萬 200萬遊行，<br />\n我相信都有人係為打卡、贖罪卷云云，<br />\n好多人依然不想付出太多，<br />\n但我哋需要佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔想太消極，<br />\n但日後岀去遊行的代價愈大，<br />\n呢班人的數目會愈少，<br />\n我哋要設法令佢哋繼續參與呢場運動。<br />\n<br />\n改變佢哋心態，好難，<br />\n但至少想大家保持「打緊仗」的心情，<br />\n唔好放棄任何一個施壓的機會。<br />\n<br />\n唱歌都可以係核彈。"},{"pid":"2dfe272cd87a1f282fa0d33ffcc24769bcc4e119","tid":1564540,"uid":197540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:09:09.000Z","msg":"TKO 唱完會拉埋大隊去修復連儂牆<br />\n我覺得呢個係凝聚力量好開始"},{"pid":"8f3c1f070574293fd12cae36819dcba8dbaea3ef","tid":1564540,"uid":85743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6ed32e4d67ffdf445b22cf262fdf08430b9b5b4","tid":1564540,"uid":246640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:50:57.000Z","msg":"講真 唱唔係問題  <b